Digit Recognition 

Implemented using DTW approach in MATLAB.

The Test folder contains 18 audio files.(<digit>1.wav/<digit>2.wav)
The Train folder contains 18 audio files.(<digit>1.wav/<digit>2.wav)
 
main_code.m - input is the name of a audio file(<digit>) and output is the best and second-best recognised digits.

cepst.m - returns the cepstrum co-efficients  of an audio file.

dtw_new.m - returns the minimum distance between the cepstrum co-efficients of the test file and each of the training files

To run : main_code(tdigit)
where tdigit is the test digit(1-9)

